casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Ranzy, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Ranzy, 134 Ohio St.3d 591, 2012-Ohio-5762.]

(No. 2012-1302 Submitted December 4, 2012 Decided December 7, 2012.) William D. Mason, Cuyahoga County Prosecuting Attorney, and Kristen L. Sobieski, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellant.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of State v. Williams, 134 Ohio St.3d 482, 2012-Ohio-5699, — N.E.2d-.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, Lanzinger, Cupp, and McGee Brown, JJ., concur. O’Donnell, J., dissents. *592Russell S. Bensing, for appellee.
